1950;;Highway 301;;American;;Andrew L. Stone;;Steve Cochran, Virginia Grey;;film noir;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Highway_301_(film);;A gang of robbers are terrorizing and robbing banks and payrolls in North Carolina, Virginia and Maryland. The gang's leader, George, seems to take particular delight in "bumping off" women who cross him. The film starts with comments from then-governors of North Carolina, Virginia and Maryland about how crime doesn't pay.